thread.title: BRIEF-Plus500 reiterates FY revenue and profit guidance
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Plus500 reiterates FY revenue and profit guidance | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Plus500 reiterates FY revenue and profit guidance
text:
Oct 12 Plus500 Ltd
* Entered Q4 2015 with positive momentum
* In nine months to 30 September 2015, revenue was $207.9m
* Still expects revenues to be ahead of 2014 but with profitability still not expected to match that of last year
* Is now also actively targeting high value customers Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
